title: Hour 3 - Anthony Slater, Marcellus Wiley
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Anthony Slater, Marcellus Wiley
description:
Dan talks to Golden State Warriors insider Anthony Slater about the Warriors bid to repeat as NBA Champions. And he checks in with former NFL DE Marcellus Wiley about Tom Brady and the rest of the NFL.
